data.description:
This 5 bedroom, 3 ½ bathroom home has two owner suites and two laundry rooms.  The common area rooms have beautiful engineered hardwood floors.  The formal dining room has coffered ceilings and decorative moldings.  The floor plan is open and spacious with the great room featuring a curved wall with windows.   This home has a gourmet kitchen with stained cabinets, granite counter tops, center island, pendant light, tile backsplash, stainless steel appliances including double ovens, 5-burner cooktop & refrigerator, stays.  The first floor owner suite has its own laundry room, full bath with tile floors and generous closet.  The half bath is located conveniently off the 2-story foyer. 
The primary owner suite is upstairs with a large sitting room with fireplace and could also function as an office, workout room, media room, etc.  There is a private full bath with a tiled shower; garden tub; dual sinks with vanity table; Venetian marble counter tops; tile floors and a huge closet.
Three guest bedrooms; guest bath and laundry room complete the upstairs.  This home has oil rubbed bronze fixtures throughout.  This home has a covered front porch; hardi-board siding; brick accents; covered back porch and fenced yard.  This home is fully landscaped with sprinklers in the front, back and sides.
